# Updating a Task

Update an unassigned, open Task.

### PUT /api/v1/tasks/1452
```json
{
  "name":"My New Task"
}
```

### Simplified Response

```json
{
  "id":1452,
  "name":"My New Task",
  "state":"opened"
}
```

